name: MySpeed
short_description: Speed test analysis software that tracks your internet speed for 30 days.
description: Speed test analysis software that tracks your internet speed for 30 days. MySpeed is a self-hosted application focused on network, tools, utility, speedtest. It can be deployed on any device via Docker Compose.
usecases: Self-host MySpeed on your home server to speed test analysis software that tracks your internet speed for 30 days without depending on third-party cloud services.
Use MySpeed to manage your network workflows privately, keeping all data under your control on local infrastructure.
